<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .header { background: #6366f1; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 20px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
      .welcome-box { background: #f0f9ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9; }
      .next-steps { background: #f3f4f6; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🎉 Welcome to No iLLusion SMM Beta!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <strong><%= @beta_signup.name %></strong>,</p>
      
      <div class="welcome-box">
        <h3>🚀 You're In!</h3>
        <p>Thanks for joining the No iLLusion SMM beta program! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
        <p><strong>What makes us different:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>🔍 <strong>Transparent</strong> - No hidden fees or surprise charges</li>
          <li>🤖 <strong>AI-Powered</strong> - Smart content generation when you need it</li>
          <li>🎯 <strong>Multi-Platform</strong> - LinkedIn, Facebook, Instagram, TikTok, YouTube</li>
          <li>💚 <strong>Privacy-First</strong> - Your content is never stored permanently</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="next-steps">
        <h3>What's Next?</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>We'll review your signup and get back to you within 24-48 hours</li>
          <li>You'll receive beta access credentials via email</li>
          <li>Join our private beta feedback group</li>
          <li>Start creating amazing social media content!</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      
      <p>In the meantime, feel free to explore our current platform at <a href="<%= ENV['APP_URL'] || 'https://smm.no-illusion.com' %>"><%= ENV['APP_DOMAIN'] || 'smm.no-illusion.com' %></a></p>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
        <strong>No iLLusion Software</strong><br>
        Building honest, transparent tools for small businesses<br>
        <a href="https://no-illusion.com">no-illusion.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>